        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Halecium scutum Clark, 1877; colony silhouettes of material from The Faroes. (A) MHNG INVE 33550; (B) BIOFAR station 699; (C) BIOFAR station 459. Scale bar: 2 cm." ;
